  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether chemotherapy induces regression in
      atherosclerotic plaques in oncologic patients already undergoing PET FDG as part of their
      routine assessment.We will use PET FDG to assess whether the inflammation in atherosclerotic
      plaques is affected by chemotherapy and anti angiogenic therapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
